description.full: This game was classified by the community with the following category scores - Violence=0/3, Sex=0/3, Mature Content=0/3. Fly across Europe in a Jump Jet, perfecting your landings on runways, helipads and ships; buy and sell goods to fund your trips; but watch out for the guns. Complete all sixteen levels and make a million to win. Now with three levels of difficulty - Normal, Difficult and Impossible.
